snippet.title: VR Pianist - Teaser Trailer | Piano Game for Virtual Reality
snippet.description:
First look at VR Pianist game, where you can play on a virtual piano.  Enjoy unique 'line-art' graphic style together with contemporary, classical and orchestral music. Maybe you are the hidden talent waiting to be discovered!

You can find more information about this project here:
https://vrpianist.com​
https://www.facebook.com/VRPianist
